text: Marina Mohnen (born 31 October 1978) is a German wheelchair basketball player. She won a silver medal at the 2008 Summer Paralympics, gold medal at the 2012 Summer Paralympics, and silver medal at the 2016 Summer Paralympics. She played at the 2010 Wheelchair Basketball World Championship, 2014 Women's World Wheelchair Basketball Championship, and 2018 Wheelchair Basketball World Championship. == References == Category:1978 births Category:Living people Category:Paralympic gold medalists for Germany Category:Paralympic silver medalists for Germany Category:German wheelchair basketball players
